            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo Pa<lb break="no" n="2"/>tron<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied> <lb n="3"/>Val<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">er</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">iu</supplied>s <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied>li<lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Verschollen. Auf der corona ein nach rechts sprengendes Tier. (B): Vulić, IMS: Z. 1/2: patron(o); Z. 6: v(otum) p(osuit) [l(ibens) m(erito)]; Z. 7 befindet sich auf dem Profil der crepido. Z. 5: Reste nicht mehr identifizierbarer Buchstaben zu erkennen.</p>
            </div>
